{"tid":2084204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海洋公園狐獴與象龜展館下月開幕　三狐獴BB獲命名茶走齋啡及鴛鴦","createTime":"2020-06-29T06:44:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T12:33:30.000Z","uid":44569,"like":3,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"e70351c75e115f0ef9d95f7b0c2ec579cd2a1962","tid":2084204,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:44:46.000Z","msg":"海洋公園今個月12日重開，園方今日公布新動物展館「小狐獴與大象龜之旅」亦將於7月1日開幕，展出20隻狐獴，包括獲港人命名的3隻年幼港產狐獴「茶走」、「齋啡」及「鴛鴦」，另亦有2隻年約15歲的亞達伯拉象龜。展館可同時容納60人，下月10日起市民亦可於網上預約下月25日至8月31日的入場名額。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2680000/2681964/franco0629a_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2680000%2F2681964%2Ffranco0629a_600.jpg&h=8ef96213&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2680000/2681964/dick0629b_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2680000%2F2681964%2Fdick0629b_600.jpg&h=cd5d95db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1cf6f34d45b19b353180d71f642ad7338e9a35f7","tid":2084204,"uid":58552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:45:53.000Z","msg":"狗也不"},{"pid":"38cde24ea814b3c89b1be5f146ff3a898cd44c98","tid":2084204,"uid":21545,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:46:10.000Z","msg":"點解唔叫鄧炳強<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a454d942fdcf75d09d949a74bcb1b2b32608b58b","tid":2084204,"uid":44569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:50:31.000Z","msg":"hakuna matata"},{"pid":"8a7f1085980385e10a89e5ace4e9494135290b9c","tid":2084204,"uid":61577,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T07:31:18.000Z","msg":"不如叫食甜筒，食郵筒同食電筒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"304192bd60f1d8805de02dffd